Rating: 4
I made this for a weeknight dinner, but I think it would also be a good "company" dish. I used low sodium soy sauce, added a little toasted sesame oil and a few flakes of red pepper. If the fish is very thick, may need to microwave a little to make sure it is cooked all the way through.

