Rating: 4
I chose to use halibut because the store I was at did not have mahi-mahi and this recipe still turned out amazing. It's so easy and so flavorful. Next time I'd add more chopped onions when making the glaze because they turn out really tasty. Also - for two large pieces fish this amount of sauce was perfect. I would think it might me a little light on the sauce for 4 pieces of fish. It's definitely a keeper though!

